abstract: >-
  Vision FSM Agent is a lightweight Python framework for building
  computer-vision-driven automation agents with finite-state-machine
  control and human-in-the-loop correction. It provides a reproducible
  synthetic demo, tests, CI, safety boundaries, and documentation for
  researchers and developers exploring visual agents in controlled local
  environments.
